<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.10">
<l>cārnta viruval viṉaikaḷuñ carittu māyap paṟṟaṟuttut</l>
<l>tīrntu taṉpāṉ maṉamvaikkat tirutti vīṭu tiruttuvā</l>
<l>ṉārnta ñāṉac cuṭarāki yakalaṅ kīḻmē laḷaviṟantu</l>
<l>nērnta vuruvā yaruvāku mivaṟṟi ṉuyirā neṭumālē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Toppling the two/big harsh karmas that had reached [me], gripping [them] by magic, cutting [them] off,</l>
<l>so that [I] finally put [my] mind on him, he who arranges release,</l>
<l>being the full glow of knowledge, goying beyond the measure of the earth below [and] above,</l>
<l>being the appropriate form he becomes formless, the tall Māl who is the life of all these.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
